:1631801,"uid":149829,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:35.000Z","msg":"夜晚一定好啲, 裝完黨鐵令到佢冇時間修復, 第二日變相罷駛, 間接幫市民罷工/遲返工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:10.000Z","msg":"但如果聽日夜晚先行動，又已經第二次做開花行動，<br />\n咁狗即係有全日時間去部署定要點樣做，<br />\n<br />\n仲有，有邊次行動，大家唔係話「入夜危險」架<br />\n<br />\n如果狗又部署好，入夜又危險，<br />\n明明紅假又夜晚先做野，就蠢左"},{"pid":"e2111bbe14a5a586278986aea0c0226d7907c2af","tid":1631801,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"其實根據一開始講既<br />\n都係假期係1PM開始架<br />\n<br />\n究竟點解連登仔又會不知不覺比人帶左去聽晚先開始架?<br />\n有多少少獨立思考啦<br />\n<br />\n你地每次行動，有邊次唔係話入夜就危險架？<br />\n<br />\n又如果，聽日夜晚先行動，又已經第二次做開花行動，<br />\n咁狗即係有全日時間去部署定要點樣做，<br />\n<br />\n咁行動一定唔會大成功<br />\n<br />\n唔該多少少獨立思考<br />\n唔好又要宜家想負皮我，事後又要比我講中左"},{"pid":"9fcd93b27ec97854f5b7ba12b8a1c61ec5ee4e2f","tid":1631801,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AsuebxZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAsuebxZ.png&h=344e2c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深水埗：南昌V walk／楓樹街遊樂場／長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n荃灣：沙咀道遊樂場／荃灣公園<br />\n葵芳：葵廣／林士德足球場／林金殿外<br />\n青衣：青衣城／<br />\n觀塘：apm／觀塘遊樂場／<br />\n黃大仙：黃大仙中心／黃大仙廣場／摩士公園<br />\n油尖旺：朗豪坊／麥花臣球場／<br />\n紅土黃何九：馬頭圍邨球場／亞皆老街球場／<br />\n將軍澳：黨鐵Popcorn／香港單車公園／<br />\n沙田：新城市廣場／車公廟站 曾大屋遊樂場<br />\n馬鞍山：新港城／鞍誠街花園／<br />\n大埔：大埔超級城／大埔中央廣場／<br />\n上水： 上水廣場／彩園廣場<br />\n屯門：屯門市廣場／屯門政府合署／新和里球場<br />\n天水圍：嘉湖銀座／天耀<br />\n元朗：Yoho／大馬路<br />\n銅鑼灣：紀利佐治街／東角道<br />\n太古：太古城中心／鰂魚涌公園／<br />\n柴小杏：柴灣橋／柴灣公園<br />\n西區：中山公園<br />\n南區：香港仔中心／<br />\n東涌：東薈城噴水池／富東商場"},{"pid":"f6f85bcd28621e438419c9212a075364c2fc68fe","tid":1631801,"uid":198133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:29.000Z","msg":"啱啱先有po 話要文宣日..."},{"pid":"363e61972dfad42343ce48854487fe41a727c110","tid":1631801,"uid":113039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2e9789e38f49df4b6de87dfaf31771fcb2cf318","tid":1631801,"uid":74958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日1PM</span>"},{"pid":"069cd5b96e3b659c8f3f3462d9195bfb6af8348c","tid":1631801,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:17.000Z","msg":"開左post 盡左責提醒大家要早d<br />\n唔好等夜晚搞到失敗<br />\n<br />\n如果多數人唔認同 唔聽<br />\n我都冇辦法<br />\n我已經提左"},{"pid":"1207ce0e01541f6e24897efeef831e9d2fef0702","tid":1631801,"uid":175806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b58992d18b83d274baa507fa24765cd768dfe69f","tid":1631801,"uid":161430,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:19:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">18區開花</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7號晚係關鍵！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">要令黨鐵全線第二日停駛</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">港豬們好耐未三罷啦</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n香港人．<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反抗</span></span><br />\n香港人．三罷</span>"},{"pid":"bca1c77eea9c6518ef84719ad09c3d8d63f7bcb1","tid":1631801,"uid":175806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f84de8deac36819b8a200a33d49d2ea2adc74c03","tid":1631801,"uid":149829,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:35.000Z","msg":"夜晚一定好啲, 裝完黨鐵令到佢冇時間修復, 第二日變相罷駛, 間接幫市民罷工/遲返工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7號晚係關鍵！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">要令黨鐵全線第二日停駛</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">港豬們好耐未三罷啦</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n香港人．<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反抗</span></span><br />\n香港人．三罷</span>"},{"pid":"968f50b1967db271091249cbf552af73bba95634","tid":1631801,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"b3d301f6021542eecf7192fdb330eb62892c3a03","tid":1631801,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:03:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1c5614a8836c6d4e30e8a0141feba660819fa091","tid":1631801,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88fc320cdce2ff1aad067522bb7d38c8e731078","tid":1631801,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:18:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非常同意</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以後只玩18區游擊開花，同埋文宣</span></span>"},{"pid":"1a23d41c5c2e4187da19950578c95f20f03788ee","tid":1631801,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2111bbe14a5a586278986aea0c0226d7907c2af","tid":1631801,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"其實根據一開始講既<br />\n都係假期係1PM開始架<br />\n<br />\n究竟點解連登仔又會不知不覺比人帶左去聽晚先開始架?<br />\n有多少少獨立思考啦<br />\n<br />\n你地每次行動，有邊次唔係話入夜就危險架？<br />\n<br />\n又如果，聽日夜晚先行動，又已經第二次做開花行動，<br />\n咁狗即係有全日時間去部署定要點樣做，<br />\n<br />\n咁行動一定唔會大成功<br />\n<br />\n唔該多少少獨立思考<br />\n唔好又要宜家想負皮我，事後又要比我講中左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:20:16.000Z","msg":"我獨立思考完既答案係夜晚搞等黨鐵冇時間回復<br />\n朝早搞有成日比佢回復仲阻到人拜山"},{"pid":"865bbc39fa1f93e154b8794650550b33c0121ac6","tid":1631801,"uid":123764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3877d3c4314dbd116b81cad24913b91e4db85ce","tid":1631801,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:32:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7db97c32bd556215888cc7ada1e35b7750279ef7","tid":1631801,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:16:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9dc252148443595652bb0362ef6d1c560eca0a4","tid":1631801,"uid":158889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:19:03.000Z","msg":"無人想做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c0a8339fb4baaca2658cbff0cafff68e06177a","tid":1631801,"uid":158889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9dc252148443595652bb0362ef6d1c560eca0a4","tid":1631801,"uid":158889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:19:03.000Z","msg":"無人想做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:19:19.000Z","msg":"唔知休乜鳩息 出理和理非都唔想 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b5ad210dfeff8604a842336f6accbfe66d913a","tid":1631801,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:19:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ae1ccdb0ec75486ba17b5564735bd716b422283","tid":1631801,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:19:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d9d75668680c69d8e9cdc9a7152644878b4096e","tid":1631801,"uid":8392,"like":0,"dislik